705643f-a.title: Brooklyn: McDonald Avenue - Avenue S
705643f-a.text:
2086 Mc Donald Ave., west side, near Ave. S. In the background, is
112th to 122 Lake Street. In the foreground, on the street, is the
shadow of the Culver Elevated Lines of the B.M.T.
April 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
